name: 2023 the 9th International Conference on Mechatronics System and Robots
content: Publication: After a careful reviewing process, all accepted papers of ICMSR 2023 will be published in ICMSR 2023 Conference Proceedings, and will be submitted for indexing to ISI/CPCI (Web of Science), Scopus, EI Compendex, Inspec (IET), Google Scholar, CAS, DOAJ, ProQuest, Zentrablatt, EBSCO etc.
